  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assess the effectiveness of utilization of endoscopically placed intra-gastric balloon in&#xD;
      obese and morbid obese adolescents combined with behavioral support for weight loss and&#xD;
      health optimization.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
